          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes"/>
          <para>
            <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM127445">Section 137</extref></citation> is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">20</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">15</amend.in>.</text>
